{"tid":314693,"cid":13,"subCid":0,"title":"時裝精入門初班：如何才稱得上是「高級訂製」？","createTime":"2017-07-09T12:38:22.000Z","updateTime":"2017-07-09T15:21:32.000Z","uid":14730,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"2ec24008c67fe8e68a0acee68c0915ab95ca1450","tid":314693,"uid":14730,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-09T12:38:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/07/09/203810_ee65f8aca4714730976bc97ec905b904.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F07%2F09%2F203810_ee65f8aca4714730976bc97ec905b904.jpg&h=0568f9fb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n每天看着網上社交平台，不斷地更新時裝消息，從剛過去的 Fall/ Winter Ready-to-wear、Cruise 早春系列，到男裝的春夏系列等等，時裝周馬不停蹄地一個接着一個，似乎沒有休息的時候，今個月終於輪到女裝秋冬高級訂製的時裝週。 <br />\n<br />\n每年的1月及7月便會在巴黎舉辦春夏、秋冬的高級訂製時裝周，而高級訂製（Haute Couture）稱得上是時裝中的精英，價值非凡之處，便是不可取代的手工藝（Craftsmanship），但並非每個品牌都能列入高級訂製，一切權利皆由法國高級時裝公會（F&eacute;d&eacute;ration Fran&ccedil;aise de la Couture）掌握，為了維持高訂質素及名譽，必須要有基本入門要求： <br />\n品牌工作室設立於巴黎 <br />\n工作室內最少有20個員工維持品牌運作 <br />\n品牌設計只能在巴黎生產 <br />\n每季系列最少有25套設計 <br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://bit.ly/2sTRdqJ\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F2sTRdqJ&d=EMnXzwzI9%2BVdAAo0RcKNFWi1w7%2FDyS2Kz%2BsYtkalU0Y%3D&h=5c0f6921\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://bit.ly/2sTRdqJ</a>"},{"pid":"c9c75045f2fedc04856c1f198013d98b919fd5e1","tid":314693,"uid":108668,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-09T15:21:32.000Z","msg":"前design jj lm"}]}